<br>
My point here is this-  The sub 50 game hasn't changed much in terms of strengths of mobs- there's a lot more zones, and fancier graphics, that's all.  HOWEVER-the average player is WAY better equipped than they were pre-Velious, let alone pre-Luclin.<br>
<br>
